# Crypto

Crypto offers a secure channel so applications can communicate safely between each other.

## Data Structures

### `Data no-CC` (object)
+ data: Clear or cipher data (string)
+ tagSize: 16 (number)
+ key: 2034F6E32958647FDFF75D265B455EBF40C80E6D597092B3A802B3E5863F878C (string)
+ iv: AD0ACC568C88C116D57B273D98FB92C0 (string)

### Data CC (object)
+ sessionId: 7ae76bf2bb4c4dc3cdffda3c5e37c9e4 (string)
+ data: Clear or cipher data (string)

### Crypto Reply (object)
+ data: Cipher or clear data (string)
+ result: SUCCESS (string)

### CC Registry (object)
+ provider: (string)
+ transactionId: (string)
+ lifespan: (number)
+ ivServerToComponent: (string)
+ keyServerToComponent: (string)
+ sessionId: (string)
+ keyComponentToServer: (string)
+ ivComponentToServer: (string)
+ tagLen: (number)

