# Group Crypto functions

### Decrypt without using CC [/crypto/decrypt]

#### Decrypt [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Data no-CC)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Crypto Reply)


### Encrypt without using CC [/crypto/encrypt]

#### Encrypt [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Data no-CC)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Crypto Reply)


### Decrypt using CC [/crypto/decryptWithCC]

#### Decrypt [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Data CC)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Crypto Reply)


### Encrypt using CC [/crypto/encryptWithCC]

#### Encrypt [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Data CC)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Crypto Reply)


### Register new CC [/crypto/registerCC]

#### Register [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (CC Registry)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result" : "SUCCESS"
        }


### Unregister existing CC [/crypto/unregisterCC]

#### Unregister [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
+ Attributes (CC Registry)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result" : "SUCCESS"
        }
